title: 140: Till [The Romantics] Have Faces
dc:creator: A.J. Hanenburg
description: Graeme wrote his grad thesis on C.S. Lewis's "Till We Have Faces." Prepare to laugh your way through an episode, because--hoo boy--Graeme's grad paper was a doozy.  It's like reading "Modeland" by Tyra Banks, but with less mascara.
itunes:author: Faceless, Anonymous, and a guy with a face so bad you can't bear to look
itunes:subtitle: I don't know where you buy 'em, but you're gonna need 'em.
